      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Management d'équipes</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Accompagnement de porteurs de projets</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Reporting</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Pack Office</span>
